aa(lp367
VHere's the idea:
p368
aVwe'll create and curate
p369
aVthe best in digital education resources.
p370
aVWe will bring those to community health workers around the world,
p371
aVincluding A.B. and Musu.
p372
aVThey'll get video lessons on giving kids vaccines
p373
aVand have online courses on spotting the next outbreak,
p374
aVso they're not stuck using flip charts.
p375
aVWe'll help these countries accredit these workers,
p376
aVso that they're not stuck remaining an under-recognized, undervalued group,
p377
aVbut become a renowned, empowered profession,
p378
aVjust like nurses and doctors.
p379
aa(lp380
VAnd we'll create a network of companies and entrepreneurs
p381
aVwho've created innovations that can save lives
p382
aVand help them connect to workers like Musu,
p383
aVso she can help better serve her community.
p384
aVAnd we'll work tirelessly to persuade governments
p385
aVto make community health workers a cornerstone of their health care plans.
p386
aVWe plan to test and prototype the academy in Liberia
p387
aVand a few other partner countries,
p388
aVand then we plan to take it global,
p389
aVincluding to rural North America.
p390
aVWith the power of this platform,
p391
aVwe believe countries can be more persuaded
p392
aVthat a health care revolution really is possible.
p393
aa(lp394
VMy dream is that this academy will contribute to the training
p395
aVof hundreds of thousands of community members
p396
aVto help bring health care to their neighbors \u2014
p397
aVthe hundreds of millions of them
p398
aVthat live in the world's most remote communities,
p399
aVfrom the forest communities of West Africa,
p400
aVto the fishing villages of rural Alaska;
p401
aVfrom the hilltops of Appalachia, to the mountains of Afghanistan.
p402
aVIf this vision is aligned with yours,
p403
aVhead to communityhealthacademy.org,
p404
aVand join this revolution.
p405
aVLet us know if you or your organization or someone you know could help us
p406
aVas we try to build this academy over the next year.
