aa(lp408
VNow, as I look out into this room,
p409
aVI realize that our journeys are not self-made;
p410
aVthey're shaped by others.
p411
aVAnd there have been so many here that have been part of this cause.
p412
aVWe're so honored to be part of this community,
p413
aVand a community that's willing to take on a cause
p414
aVas audacious as this one,
p415
aVso I wanted to offer, as I end,
p416
aVa reflection.
p417
aa(lp418
VI think a lot more about what my father taught me.
p419
aVThese days, I too have become a dad.
p420
aVI have two sons,
p421
aVand my wife and I just learned that she's pregnant with our third child.
