aVwhen we heard our baby's heartbeat.
p450
aa(lp451
VFor all of human history,
p452
aVillness has been universal and access to care has not.
p453
aVBut as a wise man once told me:
p454
aVno condition is permanent.
p455
aVIt's time.
p456
aVIt's time for us to go as far as it takes
p457
aVto change this condition together.
